1
00:00:08,041 --> 00:00:09,417
- EARTH.

2
00:00:09,458 --> 00:00:11,208
FIRE.

3
00:00:11,250 --> 00:00:12,834
AIR.

4
00:00:12,875 --> 00:00:15,375
WATER.

5
00:00:15,417 --> 00:00:16,667
ONLY THE AVATAR

6
00:00:16,709 --> 00:00:19,166
CAN MASTER
ALL FOUR ELEMENTS

7
00:00:19,208 --> 00:00:21,834
AND BRING BALANCE
TO THE WORLD.

8
00:00:27,709 --> 00:00:29,500
- THE AVATAR
HAS GONE MISSING.

9
00:00:29,542 --> 00:00:31,417
AFTER PRESIDENT RAIKO
REFUSED KORRA'S REQUEST

10
00:00:31,458 --> 00:00:33,291
TO AID THE SOUTH
IN THE WAR OF THE WATER TRIBES,

11
00:00:33,333 --> 00:00:35,000
SHE HEADED
TO THE FIRE NATION,

12
00:00:35,041 --> 00:00:37,208
SEEKING A NEW ALLY
AGAINST UNALAQ.

13
00:00:37,250 --> 00:00:39,083
BUT UNBEKNOWNST
TO HER FRIENDS,

14
00:00:39,125 --> 00:00:40,250
A DARK SPIRIT
ATTACKED KORRA

15
00:00:40,291 --> 00:00:42,458
AND DRAGGED HER
INTO THE OCEAN.

16
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:43,792
SHE HAS WASHED UP
ON A DESOLATE ISLAND

17
00:00:43,834 --> 00:00:46,875
WITH NO MEMORY
OF WHO SHE IS.

18
00:01:02,583 --> 00:01:05,000
- WE FOUND THE AVATAR
WASHED UP ONSHORE,

19
00:01:05,041 --> 00:01:07,542
BUT SHE DOESN'T
REMEMBER ANYTHING.

20
00:01:07,583 --> 00:01:09,667
- [weakly]
RAAVA.

21
00:01:09,709 --> 00:01:11,250
RAAVA.

22
00:01:11,291 --> 00:01:13,792
RAAVA.

23
00:01:16,125 --> 00:01:19,333
- A DARK ENERGY
HAS INFECTED HER.

24
00:01:19,375 --> 00:01:21,792
WE MUST PURGE IT
BEFORE IT DESTROYS

25
00:01:21,834 --> 00:01:23,625
HER AVATAR SPIRIT.

26
00:01:25,458 --> 00:01:28,333
LET THE WATERS
CLEANSE THE DARKNESS

27
00:01:28,375 --> 00:01:30,917
THAT PLAGUES
YOUR SPIRIT.

28
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:33,917
[ethereal music]

29
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:41,875
♪ ♪

30
00:01:48,917 --> 00:01:52,000
- WHO ARE YOU?
- I AM YOU.

31
00:01:52,041 --> 00:01:55,458
- WHO AM I?

32
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:58,166
- YOU ARE THE AVATAR.

33
00:01:58,208 --> 00:02:00,959
- I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THAT IS.

34
00:02:04,208 --> 00:02:06,291
- IN ORDER TO REMEMBER,

35
00:02:06,333 --> 00:02:09,000
YOU MUST REGAIN
YOUR CONNECTION

36
00:02:09,041 --> 00:02:13,333
WITH YOUR AVATAR SPIRIT.

37
00:02:13,375 --> 00:02:17,333
- IF YOU DON'T,
DARKNESS WILL ENGULF THE WORLD.

38
00:02:17,375 --> 00:02:21,375
YOU WILL DIE,
AND OUR ERA WILL END.

39
00:02:21,417 --> 00:02:24,375
- HOW DO I REGAIN
MY CONNECTION?

40
00:02:24,417 --> 00:02:28,041
- GO BACK.
RETURN TO THE BEGINNING.

41
00:02:28,083 --> 00:02:31,125
FIND RAAVA.

42
00:02:42,166 --> 00:02:43,250
- ARE YOU RAAVA?

43
00:02:43,291 --> 00:02:47,041
- NO, BUT I CAN HELP YOU
FIND HER.

44
00:02:47,083 --> 00:02:48,875
MY NAME IS WAN,
AND I WILL SHOW YOU

45
00:02:48,917 --> 00:02:51,667
HOW I BECAME
THE FIRST AVATAR.

46
00:02:57,667 --> 00:02:59,834
- NOBODY STEALS
FROM THE CHOU BROTHERS!

47
00:02:59,875 --> 00:03:02,667
- REALLY?
BECAUSE I JUST DID.

48
00:03:02,709 --> 00:03:05,208
- YOU'RE DEAD, WAN.

49
00:03:05,250 --> 00:03:08,500
- ACTUALLY, I FEEL
QUITE ALIVE.

50
00:03:10,792 --> 00:03:12,709
[Chous shouting]

51
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,417
[all grunt]

52
00:03:19,083 --> 00:03:20,709
[birds screech]

53
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:22,667
- HEY, STOP!

54
00:03:24,792 --> 00:03:27,750
[exciting music]

55
00:03:27,792 --> 00:03:35,125
♪ ♪

56
00:03:41,709 --> 00:03:44,041
- [laughs]
HEY, FELLAS.

57
00:03:44,083 --> 00:03:45,417
YOU'RE JUST IN TIME
FOR LUNCH!

58
00:03:45,458 --> 00:03:46,834
- OH!
[groans]

59
00:03:46,875 --> 00:03:50,667
- [grunting]

60
00:03:50,709 --> 00:03:54,083
- I TOLD YOU
NO ONE STEALS FROM US.

61
00:03:54,125 --> 00:03:57,083
- [laughs nervously]

62
00:03:57,125 --> 00:03:59,375
[shouts]

63
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:03,041
[groans]
[cow moos]

64
00:04:03,083 --> 00:04:04,500
[snorts]

65
00:04:04,542 --> 00:04:07,041
[groans]

66
00:04:20,458 --> 00:04:21,667
- [sighs]

67
00:04:21,709 --> 00:04:23,125
DID YOU STEAL
FROM THE CHOUS AGAIN?

68
00:04:23,166 --> 00:04:24,959
- YEAH, AND I GOT NOTHING
TO SHOW FOR IT

69
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:29,250
EXCEPT A FEW DIRTY ROLLS
AND A WHOLE LOT OF BRUISES.

70
00:04:29,291 --> 00:04:32,417
HEY, YAO,
I GOT SOME FOOD FOR YOU.

71
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:36,667
- MMM.
DELICIOUS.

72
00:04:36,709 --> 00:04:37,834
THANK YOU, WAN.

73
00:04:37,875 --> 00:04:41,834
[chirping]

74
00:04:43,291 --> 00:04:47,333
- YOU GUYS ARE
HUNGRY TOO, HUH?

75
00:04:47,375 --> 00:04:49,333
- WAN, YOU SHOULD EAT.

76
00:04:49,375 --> 00:04:51,625
- [sighs]
THEY NEED IT MORE THAN I DO.

77
00:04:51,667 --> 00:04:54,417
BESIDES, I'M TIRED
OF EATING SCRAPS.

78
00:04:54,458 --> 00:04:55,750
IF ONLY THERE WAS
SOME WAY

79
00:04:55,792 --> 00:04:57,166
TO GET
INTO THE CHOUS' FOOD CELLAR.

80
00:04:57,208 --> 00:05:00,125
WE'D BE EATING LIKE--
WELL, LIKE CHOUS.

81
00:05:00,166 --> 00:05:03,000
- IF CHOU THE ELDER CATCHES YOU
SNEAKING INTO HIS PALACE,

82
00:05:03,041 --> 00:05:04,625
YOU'LL END UP DEAD.

83
00:05:04,667 --> 00:05:07,500
OR WORSE, HE'LL BANISH YOU
TO THE SPIRIT WILDS.

84
00:05:07,542 --> 00:05:09,083
- NO, DON'T GET BANISHED.

85
00:05:09,125 --> 00:05:12,000
YOU DON'T WANT NOTHING TO DO
WITH THOSE SPIRITS.

86
00:05:12,041 --> 00:05:15,250
THEY'LL GET INSIDE YA,
SCRAMBLE UP YOUR MIND,

87
00:05:15,291 --> 00:05:20,166
TURN YA INTO THIS--
A MONSTER!

88
00:05:20,208 --> 00:05:21,875
- DON'T DO
ANYTHING CRAZY, WAN.

89
00:05:21,917 --> 00:05:24,709
YOU JUST GOTTA ACCEPT
THE WORLD IS THE WAY IT IS.

90
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:27,000
SOME PEOPLE HAVE POWER.
SOME PEOPLE DON'T.

91
00:05:27,041 --> 00:05:28,000
AND YOU DON'T.

92
00:05:28,041 --> 00:05:30,875
- [slurps]

93
00:05:30,917 --> 00:05:32,875
NOT YET, ANYWAY.

94
00:05:34,667 --> 00:05:37,041
- ARE YOU STRONG?
ARE YOU FEARLESS?

95
00:05:37,083 --> 00:05:39,875
DO YOU HAVE WHAT IT TAKES
TO BATTLE THE SPIRITS?

96
00:05:39,917 --> 00:05:41,709
THEN JOIN THE HUNT.

97
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:43,417
- COUNT ME IN.

98
00:05:45,291 --> 00:05:47,625
- [laughs]

99
00:05:47,667 --> 00:05:50,166
WE'RE GOING TO BE OUT
IN THE WILDS FOR A WEEK.

100
00:05:50,208 --> 00:05:51,959
YOU WOULDN'T LAST
TWO SECONDS.

101
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,333
- I CAN HANDLE MYSELF.

102
00:05:54,375 --> 00:05:55,750
WE ALL GET FIRE, RIGHT?

103
00:05:55,792 --> 00:05:58,625
- YEAH, BUT DO YOU KNOW
HOW TO USE IT?

104
00:05:58,667 --> 00:06:01,250
- WELL, NOT EXACTLY,
BUT I--

105
00:06:01,291 --> 00:06:02,875
- AH, LET HIM COME.

106
00:06:02,917 --> 00:06:05,000
NOT LIKE WE GOT
ANY OTHER VOLUNTEERS LINING UP.

107
00:06:05,041 --> 00:06:07,917
- ALL RIGHT.
WELCOME TO THE HUNT.

108
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:10,917
[tense music]

109
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:18,959
♪ ♪

110
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:26,000
[blows horn]

111
00:06:26,041 --> 00:06:31,542
[rumbling]

112
00:06:37,166 --> 00:06:39,041
- THE LION TURTLE.

113
00:06:39,083 --> 00:06:40,917
- GREAT GUARDIAN
OF OUR CITY,

114
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:43,291
WE ARE VENTURING
INTO THE SPIRIT WILDS

115
00:06:43,333 --> 00:06:45,417
TO BRING BACK FOOD
FOR OUR PEOPLE.

116
00:06:45,458 --> 00:06:48,750
PLEASE, GRANT US
THE POWER OF FIRE.

117
00:06:48,792 --> 00:06:52,458
- THE POWER IS YOURS
TO KEEP

118
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:56,125
UNTIL YOUR RETURN.

119
00:06:56,166 --> 00:06:58,917
- YOU'RE FIRST, KID.

120
00:07:01,125 --> 00:07:04,417
- MAY THE ELEMENT
OF FIRE

121
00:07:04,458 --> 00:07:08,000
PROTECT YOU
AGAINST THE SPIRITS.

122
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:14,875
- WHOA!
[groans]

123
00:07:14,917 --> 00:07:18,375
- JUST MAKE SURE YOU AIM
AT THE SPIRITS, NOT US, OKAY?

124
00:07:18,417 --> 00:07:20,208
- SURE THING.

125
00:07:27,125 --> 00:07:28,625
- EVERYONE STAY CLOSE.

126
00:07:28,667 --> 00:07:30,959
SPIRITS LOVE
TO PICK OFF STRAGGLERS.

127
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:33,208
- UH, GUYS?

128
00:07:33,250 --> 00:07:35,083
I DON'T THINK
I CAN DO THIS.

129
00:07:35,125 --> 00:07:36,625
- NOW, QUIT YOUR WHINING.

130
00:07:36,667 --> 00:07:38,166
WE HAVEN'T EVEN SEEN
A SPIRIT YET.

131
00:07:38,208 --> 00:07:40,834
- I THINK
I WANNA GO HOME.

132
00:07:40,875 --> 00:07:44,125
- I KNEW YOU WERE NOTHING
BUT A SNIVELING COWARD.

133
00:07:44,166 --> 00:07:46,792
GO GIVE YOUR FIRE BACK
TO THE LION TURTLE,

134
00:07:46,834 --> 00:07:49,750
AND DON'T EVER SHOW
YOUR FACE AROUND ME AGAIN.

135
00:07:57,291 --> 00:07:59,500
- WAN, YOU'RE BACK.

136
00:07:59,542 --> 00:08:02,417
- WHAT GOODIES DID YOU SNATCH
FOR US THIS TIME?

137
00:08:03,709 --> 00:08:05,458
- [gasps]
- [screams]

138
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:06,875
- WHAT DID YOU DO?

139
00:08:06,917 --> 00:08:08,917
YOU CAN'T STEAL
FROM THE LION TURTLE.

140
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:11,458
- REALLY?
BECAUSE I JUST DID.

141
00:08:21,583 --> 00:08:22,875
- YOU KNOW
IT'S FORBIDDEN

142
00:08:22,917 --> 00:08:25,125
TO BRING THE POWER
OF THE ELEMENT INTO THE CITY.

143
00:08:25,166 --> 00:08:27,166
PLEASE, GO BACK
TO THE LION TURTLE

144
00:08:27,208 --> 00:08:29,083
AND RETURN THE FIRE.

145
00:08:29,125 --> 00:08:32,792
- JAYA, IT'S TIME TO STOP
BEING SO AFRAID OF THE CHOUS

146
00:08:32,834 --> 00:08:35,542
AND SHOW THEM WE HAVE THE POWER
TO CHANGE THINGS.

147
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:45,208
HEY, CHOUS!
OPEN THE GATE, AND LET US IN.

148
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:48,667
- WHAT ARE THOSE FILTHY PEASANTS
DOING HERE?

149
00:08:48,709 --> 00:08:52,166
- DON'T WORRY, FATHER.
WE'LL TAKE CARE OF THEM.

150
00:08:52,208 --> 00:08:54,667
[door slides open]

151
00:08:54,709 --> 00:08:56,792
- HAND OVER ALL THE FOOD
YOU'RE HOARDING,

152
00:08:56,834 --> 00:08:58,500
AND WE WON'T GIVE YOU
ANY TROUBLE.

153
00:08:58,542 --> 00:09:01,542
[Chous laugh]

154
00:09:01,583 --> 00:09:03,166
- YOU'RE NOT GETTING
PAST US.

155
00:09:03,208 --> 00:09:05,792
WE HAVE THE WEAPONS.
YOU'RE POWERLESS.

156
00:09:05,834 --> 00:09:08,208
- POWERLESS, HUH?

157
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,917
[Chous groaning]

158
00:09:12,959 --> 00:09:15,417
FOLLOW ME!

159
00:09:21,250 --> 00:09:25,083
GRAB AS MUCH FOOD
AS YOU CAN.

160
00:09:25,125 --> 00:09:26,750
- MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT.

161
00:09:26,792 --> 00:09:28,959
MAYBE WE DO HAVE THE POWER
TO CHANGE THINGS.

162
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,417
- STOP RIGHT THERE!

163
00:09:30,458 --> 00:09:32,375
- LOOKS LIKE THE CHOUS
FOUND BACKUP.

164
00:09:32,417 --> 00:09:34,250
- GET EVERYONE
OUT OF HERE.

165
00:09:34,291 --> 00:09:36,959
I'LL HOLD THEM OFF.

166
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:42,917
[all grunting]

167
00:09:51,375 --> 00:09:55,291
- NO, PLEASE.
HAVE MERCY.

168
00:09:55,333 --> 00:09:57,291
WAN?

169
00:09:59,792 --> 00:10:02,834
- [groans]

170
00:10:02,875 --> 00:10:05,834
- EVEN WHEN YOU HAVE THE POWER,
YOU'RE AFRAID TO USE IT.

171
00:10:11,083 --> 00:10:14,375
- TELL ME WHO ELSE
WAS INVOLVED IN THE REBELLION,

172
00:10:14,417 --> 00:10:17,083
AND I MIGHT TAKE MERCY
ON YOU.

173
00:10:17,125 --> 00:10:18,875
- I'M NOT
TELLING YOU ANYTHING.

174
00:10:18,917 --> 00:10:22,333
- THEN, YOU'VE LEFT ME
NO CHOICE.

175
00:10:22,375 --> 00:10:26,166
WAN, YOU ARE
HEREBY BANISHED.

176
00:10:26,208 --> 00:10:29,500
- YEAH! AND GIVE BACK
THE FIRE YOU STOLE.

177
00:10:29,542 --> 00:10:32,458
- NO!
WAIT.

178
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:34,500
GREAT LION TURTLE,
I AM SORRY

179
00:10:34,542 --> 00:10:37,500
FOR STEALING THE FIRE FROM YOU,
AND I ACCEPT MY PUNISHMENT.

180
00:10:37,542 --> 00:10:38,917
BUT PLEASE,
I NEED TO BE ABLE

181
00:10:38,959 --> 00:10:40,709
TO PROTECT MYSELF
IN THE WILDS.

182
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:44,709
- NEVER AGAIN
MAY YOU RETURN

183
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:46,834
TO THIS CITY.

184
00:10:48,166 --> 00:10:50,375
BUT I WILL ALLOW YOU

185
00:10:50,417 --> 00:10:55,208
TO KEEP
THE POWER OF THE ELEMENT.

186
00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:59,208
- [grunts]

187
00:10:59,250 --> 00:11:02,208
[somber music]

188
00:11:02,250 --> 00:11:05,917
♪ ♪

189
00:11:05,959 --> 00:11:09,750
- BET HE DOESN'T LAST
TILL MORNING.

190
00:11:09,792 --> 00:11:12,417
[howling, chirping]

191
00:11:27,709 --> 00:11:30,500
- HEY, WATCH WHERE
YOU'RE STEPPING, HUMAN!

192
00:11:30,542 --> 00:11:32,542
- WHO SAID THAT?
- DOWN HERE!

193
00:11:34,166 --> 00:11:37,000
HOW'D YOU LIKE IT IF I STARTED
WALKING ALL OVER YOU?

194
00:11:37,041 --> 00:11:40,375
- [sighs]
YOU'RE JUST A LITTLE FROG.

195
00:11:40,417 --> 00:11:44,000
[shouts]
- WHO'S LITTLE NOW?

196
00:11:44,041 --> 00:11:47,291
- [gasps]

197
00:11:49,041 --> 00:11:53,333
[grunting]

198
00:11:53,375 --> 00:11:55,125
[shouts]
- [belches]

199
00:11:55,166 --> 00:11:57,625
- [panting]

200
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:09,041
[panting]

201
00:12:09,083 --> 00:12:10,083
[ominous music]

202
00:12:10,125 --> 00:12:13,333
[muffled groaning]

203
00:12:15,667 --> 00:12:19,208
[panting]

204
00:12:27,166 --> 00:12:29,542
[stomach growls]

205
00:12:29,583 --> 00:12:32,500
[sighs]

206
00:12:36,166 --> 00:12:38,583
GET OFF ME!
GET OFF ME!

207
00:12:38,625 --> 00:12:40,750
[screams]

208
00:12:40,792 --> 00:12:43,792
[groans]

209
00:12:43,834 --> 00:12:44,917
[shouts]

210
00:12:44,959 --> 00:12:46,792
[groans]

211
00:12:46,834 --> 00:12:49,792
[mystical music]

212
00:12:49,834 --> 00:12:58,583
♪ ♪

213
00:12:58,625 --> 00:13:00,709
[gasps]

214
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:04,166
- YOU ARE NOT WELCOME
IN MY OASIS, HUMAN.

215
00:13:04,208 --> 00:13:06,834
- PLEASE, HELP ME.

216
00:13:06,875 --> 00:13:09,000
I'M STARVING,
AND I HAVEN'T SLEPT ALL NIGHT.

217
00:13:09,041 --> 00:13:11,709
- NOT MY PROBLEM.

218
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:14,500
- LET ME PASS.

219
00:13:14,542 --> 00:13:19,667
- YOU DARE USE FIRE
AGAINST ME?

220
00:13:19,709 --> 00:13:21,625
NOW, BE GONE WITH YOU!

221
00:13:21,667 --> 00:13:25,792
- [groans]

222
00:13:25,834 --> 00:13:27,125
[sighs]

223
00:13:27,166 --> 00:13:29,917
[mystical music]

224
00:13:29,959 --> 00:13:33,000
[gasps]

225
00:13:33,041 --> 00:13:39,375
♪ ♪

226
00:13:39,417 --> 00:13:41,583
[spirits chirping]

227
00:13:49,667 --> 00:13:52,500
- AND WHO MIGHT YOU BE?

228
00:13:52,542 --> 00:13:55,875
- I AM BUSHY,
THE BUSH SPIRIT.

229
00:13:55,917 --> 00:13:59,542
AND I WOULD LIKE TO ENTER
YOUR OASIS.

230
00:13:59,583 --> 00:14:02,333
- VERY WELL.
YOU MAY PASS.

231
00:14:03,875 --> 00:14:06,041
[sniffs]

232
00:14:06,083 --> 00:14:07,709
WAIT A SECOND!

233
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:09,458
SOMETHING STINKS.

234
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:11,917
I KNEW I SMELLED
A HUMAN!

235
00:14:11,959 --> 00:14:14,625
- [sighs]

236
00:14:14,667 --> 00:14:17,166
[groans]

237
00:14:17,208 --> 00:14:20,542
COME ON, LET ME IN,
JUST FOR A LITTLE WHILE.

238
00:14:20,583 --> 00:14:24,458
- NO!
GO BACK TO YOUR LION TURTLE.

239
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:26,583
- BELIEVE ME,
I'D LOVE TO GO BACK HOME.

240
00:14:26,625 --> 00:14:29,000
BUT I CAN'T.
I WAS KICKED OUT.

241
00:14:29,041 --> 00:14:32,208
- THAT'S TOO BAD.
- POOR HUMAN.

242
00:14:32,250 --> 00:14:34,291
- DON'T PITY HIM.

243
00:14:34,333 --> 00:14:36,125
HE'S JUST LIKE
EVERY OTHER HUMAN:

244
00:14:36,166 --> 00:14:37,792
UGLY, DESTRUCTIVE,

245
00:14:37,834 --> 00:14:40,583
AND LACKING ANY RESPECT
FOR NATURE.

246
00:14:40,625 --> 00:14:44,208
- WHO ARE YOU CALLING UGLY,
UGLY?

247
00:14:44,250 --> 00:14:45,834
- HMM.

248
00:14:45,875 --> 00:14:47,667
- IF YOU CAN'T GO BACK
TO YOUR CITY,

249
00:14:47,709 --> 00:14:49,417
THEN YOU SHOULD GO LIVE
IN ANOTHER ONE.

250
00:14:49,458 --> 00:14:51,583
- WHAT?
THERE ARE OTHER LION TURTLES?

251
00:14:51,625 --> 00:14:53,041
- "THERE ARE
OTHER LION TURTLES?"

252
00:14:53,083 --> 00:14:55,375
OF COURSE THERE ARE,
DOZENS OF THEM!

253
00:14:55,417 --> 00:14:58,333
BOY, YOU HUMANS
ARE STUPID TOO.

254
00:14:58,375 --> 00:15:00,125
- SO WHICH WAY
TO THE NEAREST LION TURTLE CITY?

255
00:15:00,166 --> 00:15:02,375
- HMM.

256
00:15:02,417 --> 00:15:04,000
I THINK
IT'S ON THE OTHER SIDE

257
00:15:04,041 --> 00:15:06,166
OF NONE-OF-YOUR-BUSINESS VALLEY.

258
00:15:06,208 --> 00:15:11,041
[laughs]

259
00:15:11,083 --> 00:15:12,375
[sighs]

260
00:15:12,417 --> 00:15:13,834
- REAL FUNNY.

261
00:15:13,875 --> 00:15:15,166
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I DON'T NEED YOUR HELP.

262
00:15:15,208 --> 00:15:17,583
I'LL FIND IT MYSELF.

263
00:15:19,667 --> 00:15:20,583
- GOOD LUCK!

264
00:15:20,625 --> 00:15:23,583
[gentle music]

265
00:15:23,625 --> 00:15:29,709
♪ ♪

266
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:32,333
[stomach growls]

267
00:15:32,375 --> 00:15:34,583
[cat-deer growls]

268
00:15:39,125 --> 00:15:41,750
[cat-deer whimpers]

269
00:15:41,792 --> 00:15:42,750
- [sighs]

270
00:15:42,792 --> 00:15:44,250
[cat-deer growls]

271
00:15:44,291 --> 00:15:46,375
IT'S OKAY.
I'M GONNA GET YOU OUT OF THERE.

272
00:15:49,834 --> 00:15:52,041
- FINALLY,
WE CAUGHT SOMETHING.

273
00:15:52,083 --> 00:15:54,583
GET IT DOWN.

274
00:15:54,625 --> 00:15:55,625
- BACK OFF.

275
00:15:55,667 --> 00:15:58,208
- WAN?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

276
00:15:58,250 --> 00:15:59,583
- I'M SAVING
THIS ANIMAL.

277
00:15:59,625 --> 00:16:01,875
- THAT ANIMAL'S
OUR DINNER.

278
00:16:01,917 --> 00:16:04,000
NOW, GET OUT
OF THE WAY.

279
00:16:04,041 --> 00:16:06,625
- NO.

280
00:16:06,667 --> 00:16:09,625
[dramatic music]

281
00:16:09,667 --> 00:16:12,125
♪ ♪

282
00:16:15,208 --> 00:16:18,166
[dramatic music]

283
00:16:18,208 --> 00:16:25,000
♪ ♪

284
00:16:25,041 --> 00:16:26,375
- AHH!

285
00:16:26,417 --> 00:16:30,458
HE--HELP!
HELP!

286
00:16:38,625 --> 00:16:40,834
- GET 'EM OFF!
GET 'EM OFF!

287
00:16:40,875 --> 00:16:43,917
AHH!

288
00:16:43,959 --> 00:16:45,625
- [shouts]

289
00:16:45,667 --> 00:16:48,041
[groans]

290
00:16:48,083 --> 00:16:51,583
- WELL, LOOKS LIKE
YOU'RE ALL OUT OF TRICKS, WAN.

291
00:16:55,875 --> 00:17:00,000
- I REALLY HATE HUMANS!

292
00:17:00,041 --> 00:17:04,166
- NO, NO.
[screams]

293
00:17:04,208 --> 00:17:05,917
- [groans]

294
00:17:05,959 --> 00:17:09,125
[sighs]

295
00:17:09,166 --> 00:17:11,500
[screams]

296
00:17:11,542 --> 00:17:13,375
- I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S SCREAMING ABOUT.

297
00:17:13,417 --> 00:17:15,041
HE'S BETTER-LOOKING NOW.

298
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:23,458
- I FEEL GREAT.
WHAT'S IN THIS WATER?

299
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:26,500
- IT HAS
SPECIAL HEALING PROPERTIES.

300
00:17:26,542 --> 00:17:28,500
- THANKS.

301
00:17:28,542 --> 00:17:31,458
SO WHAT DID YOU DO
TO THAT HUNTER?

302
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:33,083
- SPIRITS ARE ABLE
TO TAKE OVER

303
00:17:33,125 --> 00:17:35,417
A HUMAN BODY
FOR A SHORT TIME.

304
00:17:35,458 --> 00:17:37,125
IF I STAYED IN THERE
ANY LONGER,

305
00:17:37,166 --> 00:17:40,166
I WOULD'VE KILLED HIM,
WHICH I DID CONSIDER.

306
00:17:40,208 --> 00:17:41,500
- THANKS FOR SAVING
MY NECK.

307
00:17:41,542 --> 00:17:44,041
BUT WHY'D YOU DO IT?

308
00:17:44,083 --> 00:17:46,875
- I SAW YOU SAVE THE CAT-DEER
FROM THOSE HUNTERS.

309
00:17:46,917 --> 00:17:49,041
I'VE NEVER SEEN
SUCH AN ACT

310
00:17:49,083 --> 00:17:51,208
OF SELFLESSNESS
FROM A HUMAN BEFORE.

311
00:17:51,250 --> 00:17:52,792
- TOLD YOU
I WASN'T LIKE THE OTHERS.

312
00:17:52,834 --> 00:17:56,083
- GUESS I UNDERESTIMATED YOU,
HUMAN.

313
00:17:56,125 --> 00:17:58,959
- ARE YOU OFF TO FIND
ANOTHER LION TURTLE CITY?

314
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:00,667
- I WAS.

315
00:18:00,709 --> 00:18:03,208
BUT I THINK I'VE HAD ENOUGH
OF HUMANS FOR A WHILE.

316
00:18:03,250 --> 00:18:04,333
I'VE DECIDED
TO STAY HERE

317
00:18:04,375 --> 00:18:06,250
AND LEARN THE WAYS
OF THE SPIRITS.

318
00:18:06,291 --> 00:18:08,500
- WHAT A GREAT IDEA.
- THAT'LL BE FUN.

319
00:18:08,542 --> 00:18:09,709
- OH, NOW, NOW,
HOLD ON.

320
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:12,375
A HUMAN LIVING
WITH SPIRITS?

321
00:18:12,417 --> 00:18:13,834
IT'S NEVER BEEN DONE.

322
00:18:13,875 --> 00:18:14,792
- FIRST TIME
FOR EVERYTHING, RIGHT?

323
00:18:14,834 --> 00:18:16,500
- HMM.

324
00:18:16,542 --> 00:18:18,792
I GUESS
WE CAN TRY IT.

325
00:18:18,834 --> 00:18:21,291
I'VE NEVER HAD A HUMAN
AS A PET BEFORE.

326
00:18:21,333 --> 00:18:23,834
I THINK
I'LL CALL YOU "STINKY."

327
00:18:23,875 --> 00:18:25,542
- THE NAME IS WAN.

328
00:18:25,583 --> 00:18:27,917
- STINKY IS
MORE ACCURATE.

329
00:18:31,625 --> 00:18:33,250
- WHAT HAPPENED
IN THE WILDS?

330
00:18:33,291 --> 00:18:34,458
WHERE ARE THE OTHERS?

331
00:18:34,500 --> 00:18:36,834
- GONE.
SPIRITS TOOK THEM.

332
00:18:36,875 --> 00:18:38,750
THEY WERE PROTECTING
THAT KID WAN

333
00:18:38,792 --> 00:18:41,041
LIKE HE WAS
ONE OF THEIR OWN.

334
00:18:41,083 --> 00:18:43,667
- DID YOU HEAR THAT?
WAN'S STILL ALIVE.

335
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:48,667
- [growls]

336
00:18:52,041 --> 00:18:53,542
[applause]

337
00:18:53,583 --> 00:18:56,542
[dramatic music]

338
00:18:56,583 --> 00:18:59,458
♪ ♪

339
00:18:59,500 --> 00:19:01,709
- AND THE WAY WAN
MOVES FIRE,

340
00:19:01,750 --> 00:19:04,041
IT'S LIKE NOTHING
I'VE EVER SEEN.

341
00:19:04,083 --> 00:19:08,250
HE USES IT LIKE
IT'S AN EXTENSION OF HIS BODY.

342
00:19:08,291 --> 00:19:10,667
[groaning]

343
00:19:17,166 --> 00:19:20,834
[all cheering]

344
00:19:25,875 --> 00:19:28,333
- WAN HAS PROVEN
THAT WITH THE POWER OF FIRE,

345
00:19:28,375 --> 00:19:30,500
ANYONE CAN SURVIVE
IN THE WILDS.

346
00:19:30,542 --> 00:19:32,041
WE DON'T HAVE TO LIVE

347
00:19:32,083 --> 00:19:34,875
UNDER CHOU THE ELDER'S RULES
ANYMORE,

348
00:19:34,917 --> 00:19:37,333
SO I SAY WE LEAVE THIS CITY
AND START OVER.

349
00:19:37,375 --> 00:19:38,625
WHO'S WITH ME?

350
00:19:38,667 --> 00:19:42,458
[all cheering]

351
00:19:42,500 --> 00:19:45,458
[gentle music]

352
00:19:45,500 --> 00:19:53,417
♪ ♪

353
00:20:00,208 --> 00:20:01,250
- YOU READY TO GO, MULA?

354
00:20:01,291 --> 00:20:03,458
- YOU SURE
YOU WANT TO LEAVE?

355
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:06,041
- YES, IT'S TIME I SEE
THE REST OF THE WORLD

356
00:20:06,083 --> 00:20:07,959
AND FIND
THE OTHER LION TURTLE CITIES.

357
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:11,667
- I'M PROUD TO CALL YOU
MY FRIEND, STINKY.

358
00:20:11,709 --> 00:20:13,291
- [sighs]
THANK YOU FOR EVERYTHING.

359
00:20:13,333 --> 00:20:15,125
GOOD-BYE, EVERYONE.

360
00:20:15,166 --> 00:20:18,083
- WE'LL MISS YOU.

361
00:20:18,125 --> 00:20:25,792
♪ ♪

362
00:20:38,667 --> 00:20:39,750
- [whimpers]

363
00:20:39,792 --> 00:20:41,250
- [groans]

364
00:20:41,291 --> 00:20:44,166
- THE ALL-POWERFUL SPIRITS
ARE BATTLING.

365
00:20:44,208 --> 00:20:46,959
- THEY'RE GONNA WIPE OUT
THE ENTIRE VALLEY!

366
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:49,959
[tense music]

367
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:58,166
♪ ♪

368
00:20:58,208 --> 00:20:59,166
[Mula growls]

369
00:20:59,208 --> 00:21:04,959
[spirits grunting]

370
00:21:12,959 --> 00:21:15,375
- STOP,
OR YOU'LL DESTROY EVERYTHING!

371
00:21:15,417 --> 00:21:18,375
- THIS DOESN'T
CONCERN YOU, HUMAN!

372
00:21:18,417 --> 00:21:19,625
- IT DOES
WHEN THE LIVES

373
00:21:19,667 --> 00:21:22,959
OF SPIRITS AND ANIMALS
ARE IN DANGER.

374
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:25,333
- IF YOU'RE A FRIEND
TO SPIRITS,

375
00:21:25,375 --> 00:21:29,083
THEN USE YOUR FIRE TO HELP ME
BREAK FREE.

376
00:21:29,125 --> 00:21:31,959
- DON'T INVOLVE THE HUMAN.
THIS IS BETWEEN US.

377
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:35,041
- PLEASE, SAVE ME.

378
00:21:35,083 --> 00:21:39,041
SHE HAS TORMENTED ME
FOR 10,000 YEARS.

379
00:21:39,083 --> 00:21:42,333
- 10,000 YEARS?

380
00:21:42,375 --> 00:21:45,041
LET HIM GO!

381
00:21:45,083 --> 00:21:46,792
[shouts]

382
00:21:59,083 --> 00:22:01,834
- [screams]

383
00:22:01,875 --> 00:22:04,125
- THANK YOU, HUMAN.

384
00:22:04,166 --> 00:22:08,750
YOU HAVE PERFORMED
A GREAT SERVICE FOR THE SPIRITS.

385
00:22:12,834 --> 00:22:16,000
- DO YOU REALIZE
WHAT YOU'VE DONE?

386
00:22:16,041 --> 00:22:19,208
- YEAH, I HELPED A SPIRIT
WHO WAS BEING BULLIED BY YOU.

387
00:22:19,250 --> 00:22:21,542
- YOU ARE
GRAVELY MISTAKEN.

388
00:22:21,583 --> 00:22:24,000
I WAS KEEPING HIM
UNDER CONTROL.

389
00:22:24,041 --> 00:22:25,625
- AND WHAT GIVES YOU
THE RIGHT?

390
00:22:25,667 --> 00:22:28,750
- YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW WHO I AM,
DO YOU?

391
00:22:28,792 --> 00:22:30,917
- SHOULD I?
- YES.

392
00:22:30,959 --> 00:22:33,917
MY NAME IS RAAVA.

393
00:22:33,959 --> 00:22:36,625
THAT SPIRIT YOU FREED
IS VAATU.

394
00:22:36,667 --> 00:22:40,333
HE IS THE FORCE
OF DARKNESS AND CHAOS.

395
00:22:40,375 --> 00:22:43,500
I AM THE FORCE
OF LIGHT AND PEACE.

396
00:22:43,542 --> 00:22:45,250
SINCE THE BEGINNING
OF TIME,

397
00:22:45,291 --> 00:22:47,750
WE HAVE BATTLED
OVER THE FATE OF THIS WORLD.

398
00:22:47,792 --> 00:22:50,959
AND FOR THE PAST
10,000 YEARS,

399
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:53,417
I HAVE KEPT DARKNESS
UNDER CONTROL

400
00:22:53,458 --> 00:22:55,542
AND THE WORLD
IN BALANCE,

401
00:22:55,583 --> 00:22:57,166
UNTIL YOU CAME ALONG.

402
00:22:57,208 --> 00:23:00,542
- SO BY FREEING VAATU,

403
00:23:00,583 --> 00:23:02,375
I LET CHAOS
INTO THE WORLD?

404
00:23:02,417 --> 00:23:03,709
- PRECISELY.

405
00:23:03,750 --> 00:23:05,583
THE HUMAN
AND SPIRIT REALMS

406
00:23:05,625 --> 00:23:07,625
ARE HEADED
TOWARD ANNIHILATION,

407
00:23:07,667 --> 00:23:10,333
AND IT'S ALL YOUR FAULT.

408
00:23:13,917 --> 00:23:16,834
- RAAVA, I FOUND YOU.
